title: Adobe Analytics ExperienceEvent Full Extension
description: Adobe Analytics ExperienceEvent full extension. Contains all Solution added fields.

num.title: Session Number
num.description: Current session number for the end-user.

depth.title: Session Depth
depth.description: Current session depth (eg page number) for the end-user.

timestamp.title: Session Entry Timestamp
timestamp.description: The timestamp at the entry into this session. Milliseconds since midnight of January 1, 1970.

search.title: Session Entry Search
search.description: The information related to web or mobile search at the entry of this session.

web.title: Session Entry Web
web.description: The information related to web page, link, and referrer at the entry of this session.

firstTimestamp.title: End-User First Timestamp
firstTimestamp.description: The timestamp for the first ExperienceEvent for this end-user. Milliseconds since midnight of January 1, 1970.

firstWeb.title: End-User First Web Details
firstWeb.description: The information related to web page, link, and referrer from the first ExperienceEvent for this end-user.

stateProvince.title: state
stateProvince.description: Client supplied state or province location.

browserID.title: Browser ID
browserID.description: The Adobe Analytics identifier for the browser used.

operatingSystemID.title: Operating System ID
operatingSystemID.description: The Adobe Analytics identifier of the operating system used.
